</span></div><div>the funniest stuff I've seen with the line "I have a boyfriend"!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9LSbcWl.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Aakash Singh.. he's uncanny the way he sizes up people! and that instant "ay, shut up" just cracked me up.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JSVCo1i.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>i honestly never knew Jamie Foxx was so funny. this clip just gets better as it goes on. i like Graham Norton, he brings out the quirkiness of his guests.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lXu1Q5j.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>intergalactic dad jokes! this whispering just makes this so much better... the whole channel is inspired https://youtube.com/@plutopiaworld. thought some of you would dig it too.

that's it. just wanted to share what made me grin despite having no luck with job hunting for some months and a family member being hospitalised. hope y'all find something to cheer you up too.

eta: thanks for the award. send funny stuff if you can!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iVlTnNH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dicot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Otter Needs Help</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gD16vjk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U4gI6SF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gD16vjk</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ohthefunk]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Pixar movie IRL</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GVblGe3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iVEG7cL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hot air balloons at sunrise in Turkey</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GVblGe3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BlakeNorthcott]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cowinkeedink or nah?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aOHhAm7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m6U7hyJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aOHhAm7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>my favorite Noodle videos this year so far</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EK7Z7RR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AjCQOMd.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cWyJtCU.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/g7k1Hku.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WOIAlFg.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EK7Z7RR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[friendlynoodles]]></dc:c